        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>Eagle Island</placeName> <date when="1836-07-10">July 10th 1836</date></p>

<p><persName>Genl S F Austin</persName></p>

<p>Dear Sir</p>

<p>I am anxious to see you and since I have heard of your return I have
been endeavouring to do so. I have just returned from <placeName>Columbia </placeName>where
I expected to meet you and would now go to <placeName>Velasco </placeName>if I was certain you
was there If possible I would be glad if you would come up, or 
otherwise name the place where I can see you in a few days</p>

<p><persName>John A Wharton</persName></p>



        </div1>
